Threat detection summary
SELECT threat_label, COUNT(*) AS count
FROM logs
GROUP BY threat_label
ORDER BY count DESC;
+----------------+-------+
| threat_label   | count |
+----------------+-------+
| NONE           | 3     |
| SQL_INJECTION  | 1     |
| BRUTE_FORCE    | 1     |
+----------------+-------+

Suspicious activity (blocked requests)
SELECT * FROM logs
WHERE action = 'DENY';
